snippet.title: CsvJdbc - CSV file JDBC driver
snippet.description: A read-only JDBC driver for Java that uses Comma Separated Value (CSV) files as database tables. Ideal for writing data import programs and conversion programs.

snippet.title: Open Asset Import Library
snippet.description: Importer library to import assets from different common 3D file formats such as Collada, Blend, Obj, X, 3DS, LWO, MD5, MD2, MD3, MDL, MS3D and a lot of other formats. The data is stored in an own in-memory data-format, which can be easily processed.

snippet.title: Excel php search tool
snippet.description: PHP module for CMS Sitebill for import/export Excel-files with realty adverts

snippet.title: Super CSV
snippet.description: A fast, programmer-friendly, free CSV library for Java

snippet.title: Excel Writer
snippet.description: A standalone, portable package for producing Excel spreadsheets

snippet.title: Pdf Split and Merge with Bookmark Import
snippet.description: PDF merging with bookmarks and pagination

snippet.title: CSV Loader
snippet.description: CSV Loader is a Java application that loads data from Excel CSV files into Oracle, MySQL, and PostgreSQL relational databases. IMPORTANT: After downloading, please visit http://csvloader.sourceforge.net for installation instructions. The source files are available at https://code.google.com/p/csvldr. Use Netbeans IDE to open the project.

snippet.title: Free Huge CSV Splitter
snippet.description: you can use this tool to split huge csv file by line count.

snippet.title: OpenXLS Java Excel Spreadsheet SDK
snippet.description: OpenXLS is the open source version of ExtenXLS -- a best-in-class Java spreadsheet SDK that allows you to read, modify and create Excel-compatible spreadsheets from your Java applications. Supports Excel 97-2012 file formats.
